{"link": "http://www.eclipse.org/paho/articles/talkingsmall/", "text": "cd org.eclipse.paho.mqtt.python\nmake\nmake install"}
{"link": "http://www.eclipse.org/paho/articles/talkingsmall/", "text": "With the Paho MQTT library built, we can return to our Python code and start adding the basic elements. The first thing to do is to import the library:"}
{"link": "http://www.eclipse.org/paho/articles/talkingsmall/", "text": "import Adafruit_BBIO.ADC as ADC\nimport time\nimport paho.mqtt.client as mqtt"}
