{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/committees/mqtt/charter.php", "text": "The OASIS Message Queuing Telemetry Transport (MQTT) TC approved a revised charter on 25 April 2016 ("}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/committees/mqtt/charter.php", "text": "https://www.oasis-open.org/committees/ballot.php?id=2925"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/committees/mqtt/charter.php", "text": ") and began work under its new charter on 16 June 2016."}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/committees/mqtt/charter.php", "text": "The previous charter can be found at"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/committees/mqtt/charter.php", "text": "https://lists.oasis-open.org/archives/mqtt/201302/msg00000.html"}
