{"link": "https://www.eclipse.org/paho/clients/c/", "text": "Command line utilities are included, paho_c_pub and paho_c_sub for publishing and subscribing respectively.  \nTo start the publishing program, connecting to the Eclipse IoT sandbox:"}
{"link": "https://www.eclipse.org/paho/clients/c/", "text": "paho_c_pub -t my_topic --connection iot.eclipse.org:1883"}
{"link": "https://www.eclipse.org/paho/clients/c/", "text": "Then each line you type will be sent as a message.  To receive messages, in a similar way:"}
{"link": "https://www.eclipse.org/paho/clients/c/", "text": "paho_c_sub -t my_topic --connection iot.eclipse.org:1883"}
{"link": "https://www.eclipse.org/paho/clients/c/", "text": "To see the full list of options, type the utility name without any options."}
