{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Wrapping the existing Java-API was rather painful but gave me great flexibility to create an idiomatic Scala-API."}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "But an approach like that comes with a price:"}
