{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "The same conditions apply to a Server when it\r\nsends a PUBLISH with QoS > 0"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[MQTT-2.3.1-4]"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "A PUBLISH Packet MUST NOT\r\ncontain a Packet Identifier if its QoS value is set to 0"}
