{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "I hope to share more about myself and my general views on software development in 2019. I hope to write some blogs about the Smalltalk programming language and environment. I will keep blogging about Eclipse Collections and Java as well I\u2019m sure, especially as we look to the future after the 10.0 release. Java has been changing a lot since Java 8 was released. There is a lot of excitement again around this now twenty four year old programming language."}
