{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Wrap up"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "With two weeks to go until the end of Summer of Code 2019 there is not that much left to do for me to fulfill my proposed timeline.\nOne major thing that is still missing are automated tests.\nI have started work on it now and will work on that for the last two weeks."}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "This will also be my last update post on Summer of Code as the next post will be a summary of my whole summer."}
