{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "is a popular JavaScript library created by Facebook widely used for developing web user interfaces."}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "In this post we introduce a tutorial on how to develop a chess game based on React, JSX and N4JS. The full tutorial is available (and playable) at"}
