{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "The topics of this release in a nutshell were:"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Memory improvements for huge amounts (multi million) of digital twins which are held in memory"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Adding metrics and logging around the connectivity feature in order to enable being able to operate connections to foreign systems/brokers via APIs"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Enhancing Ditto\u2019s connectivity feature by additionally being able to connect to Apache Kafka"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Performance improvements of Ditto\u2019s search\u00a0functionality"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Stabilization of cluster bootstrapping"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Refactoring of how the services\u00a0configurations are\u00a0determined"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Addition of a Helm template in order to simplify Kubernetes based deployments"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Contributions from Microsoft in order to ease operating Eclipse Ditto on Microsoft Azure"}
