{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "If the Server accepts a connection with\r\nCleanSession set to 1, the Server MUST set Session Present to 0 in the CONNACK\r\npacket in addition to setting a zero return code in the CONNACK packet"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[MQTT-3.2.2-1]"}
