{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "The\r\nvalue of the DUP flag from an incoming PUBLISH packet is not propagated when\r\nthe PUBLISH Packet is sent to subscribers by the Server. The DUP flag in the\r\noutgoing PUBLISH packet is set independently to the incoming PUBLISH packet,\r\nits value MUST be determined solely by whether the outgoing PUBLISH packet is a\r\nretransmission"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[MQTT-3.3.1-3]"}
