{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "A PUBLISH Packet\r\nMUST NOT have both QoS bits set to 1. If a Server or Client receives a PUBLISH Packet\r\nwhich has both QoS bits set to 1 it MUST close the Network Connection"}
