{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "The code is attached to"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Bug 547665"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": ". The prototype looks quite promising."}
