{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "It MUST set the RETAIN flag to 0 when a PUBLISH\r\nPacket is sent to a Client because it matches an established subscription\r\nregardless of how the flag was set in the message it received"}
