{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "A\r\nPUBLISH Packet with a RETAIN flag set to 1 and a payload containing zero bytes\r\nwill be processed as normal by the Server and sent to Clients with a\r\nsubscription matching the topic name. Additionally any existing retained message\r\nwith the same topic name MUST be removed and any future subscribers for the\r\ntopic will not receive a retained message"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[MQTT-3.3.1-10]"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "\u201cAs normal\u201d means that the RETAIN flag is not set\r\nin the message received by existing Clients."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "A\r\nzero byte retained message MUST NOT be stored as a retained message on the\r\nServer"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[MQTT-3.3.1-11]"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "If\r\nthe RETAIN flag is 0, in a PUBLISH Packet sent by a Client to a Server, the\r\nServer MUST NOT store the message and MUST NOT remove or replace any existing\r\nretained message"}
