{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "For example:"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Jakarta Batch provides describes a means for executing and managing batch processes in Jakarta EE applications."}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "and:"}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "Jakarta Message Service describes a means for Jakarta EE applications to create, send, and receive messages via loosely coupled, reliable asynchronous communication services."}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "For the scope statement, you can assume that the reader has a rudimentary understanding of the field. It\u2019s reasonable, for example, to expect the reader to understand what \u201cbatch processing\u201d means."}
{"link": "https://planeteclipse.org/planet/", "text": "I should note that the two examples presented above are just examples of form. I\u2019m pretty sure that they make sense, but defer to the project teams to work with their communities to sort out the final form."}
