{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "4.7.1.3 Single level\r\nwildcard"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "The plus sign (\u2018+\u2019 U+002B) is a wildcard character that\r\nmatches only one topic level."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "The single-level wildcard\r\ncan be used at any level in the Topic Filter, including first and last levels.\r\nWhere it is used it MUST occupy an entire level of the filter"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[MQTT-4.7.1-3]"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": ". It can be used at more than one level\r\nin the Topic Filter and can be used in conjunction with the multilevel\r\nwildcard."}
