{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "4.7.2"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "Topics beginning with $"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "The Server MUST NOT match\r\nTopic Filters starting with a wildcard character (# or +) with Topic Names\r\nbeginning with a $ character"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[MQTT-4.7.2-1]"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": ".\r\nThe Server SHOULD prevent Clients from using such Topic Names to exchange\r\nmessages with other Clients. Server implementations MAY use Topic Names that\r\nstart with a leading $ character for other purposes."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "Non normative comment"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "\u00b7"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/standards", "text": "HTML"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/standards", "text": "PDF"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/standards", "text": "DOCX"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/standards", "text": "Distribution ZIP File"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/standards", "text": "OASIS Cross-Enterprise Security and Privacy Authorization (XSPA) TC"}
