{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "A subscription to \u201c+/monitor/Clients\u201d will not receive any\r\nmessages published to \u201c$SYS/monitor/Clients\u201d"}
