{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "A subscription to \u201c$SYS/#\u201d will receive messages published to\r\ntopics beginning with \u201c$SYS/\u201d"}
