{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "For a Client to receive messages from topics that begin with $SYS/\r\nand from topics that don\u2019t begin with a $, it has to subscribe to both \u201c#\u201d and\r\n\u201c$SYS/#\u201d"}
