{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "As a transport protocol, MQTT is concerned only with message\r\ntransmission and it is the implementer\u2019s responsibility to provide appropriate\r\nsecurity features. This is commonly achieved by using TLS"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[RFC5246]"}
