{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "In addition to technical security issues there could also be\r\ngeographic (e.g. U.S.-EU SafeHarbor"}
