{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "5.4 Implementation notes"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "There are many security concerns to consider when\r\nimplementing or using MQTT. The following section should not be considered a\r\n\u201ccheck list\u201d."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "An implementation might want to achieve some, or all, of the\r\nfollowing:"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "5.4.1 Authentication of Clients\r\nby the Server"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "The CONNECT Packet contains Username and Password fields.\r\nImplementations can choose how to make use of the content of these fields. They\r\nmay provide their own authentication mechanism, use an external authentication\r\nsystem such as LDAP"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "[RFC4511]"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/standards", "text": ". Latest version:"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/standards", "text": "https://docs.oasis-open.org/dss-x/dss-md/v1.0/dss-md-v1.0.html"}
{"link": "https://www.oasis-open.org/standards", "text": "."}
