{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "Server implementations detecting unwelcome behavior might\r\nimplement a dynamic block list based on identifiers such as IP address or\r\nClient Identifier."}
