{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "should allow for session renegotiation to establish new cryptographic\r\n     parameters (replace session keys, change cipher suites, change\r\n     authentication credentials)."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "Servers may disconnect Clients and require them to\r\n     re-authenticate with new credentials."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "Constrained devices and Clients on constrained networks can\r\nmake use of TLS session resumption"}
