{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "Implementers and solution designers might wish to consider\r\nsecurity as a set of profiles which can be applied to the MQTT protocol. An\r\nexample of a layered security hierarchy is presented below."}
