{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "When using the clear communication profile, the MQTT\r\nprotocol runs over an open network with no additional secure communication\r\nmechanisms in place."}
