{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "When using the secured network communication profile, the MQTT\r\nprotocol runs over a physical or virtual network which has security controls\r\ne.g., VPNs or physically secure network."}
