{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "The MQTT specification defines conformance for MQTT Client\r\nimplementations and MQTT Server implementations."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "An MQTT implementation MAY conform as both an MQTT Client\r\nand MQTT Server implementation."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "A"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "Server that both accepts inbound connections and\r\nestablishes outbound connections to other Servers MUST conform as both an MQTT\r\nClient and MQTT Server"}
