{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "Conformant implementations\r\nMUST NOT require the use of any extensions defined outside of this\r\nspecification in order to interoperate with any other conformant implementation"}
