{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "An MQTT Server conforms to this specification only if it\r\nsatisfies all the statements below:"}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "1. The format of all Control Packets that the Server sends\r\nmatches the format described in Chapter 2 and Chapter 3."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "2. It follows the Topic matching rules described in Section 4.7."}
{"link": "http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-os.html", "text": "3. It satisfies all of the MUST level requirements in the\r\nfollowing chapters that are identified except for those that only apply to the Client"}
